data.description: Wow, great home in a quiet neighborhood!  RV parking available and no HOA!!    Enter the warm and inviting home with living room and bay window, family room and kitchen, open concept.  Walkout to deck, mature landscaping and private backyard featuring 2 great sheds for storing your toys.  Upper level features 2 bedrooms with new carpet and full size bath.  Lower cozy level features a wood stove insert.  Can't wait for those winter evenings to cozy up in this space!!  Also features bedroom and 3/4 upgraded bath. Bonus space in the basement, new carpet!!   Lovely home on corner lot, don't miss your chance to see this great home!!
